                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-block scroll-animate">
                <div class="feature-content">
                    <h3>From Fear to Frankness</h3>
                    <h4>Built on a Foundation of Guaranteed Anonymity</h4>
                    <p>Trust is everything in culture work. Unlike other platforms where employees worry about de-anonymization, Hoogly's architecture guarantees true anonymity, encouraging honest, unfiltered feedback.</p>
                    <div class="feature-visual">
                        <div class="mockup-container">
                            <div class="privacy-shield">
                                <div class="shield-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
