            <h2 class="section-title scroll-animate">Designed for the Modern Head of People</h2>
            
            <div class="founder-quote scroll-animate">
                <blockquote>
                    "As a founder, I saw firsthand how traditional surveys created more problems than they solved. 
                    We built Hoogly because People leaders at fast-growing companies don't need another dashboard; 
                    they need a direct line to the truth and the tools to act on it instantly."
                </blockquote>
                <cite>‚Äî Hoogly Team</cite>
            </div>

            <div class="testimonial scroll-animate">
                <blockquote>
                    "Hoogly is a complete game changer, when it comes to employee engagement"
                </blockquote>
