            <h2 class="cta-title scroll-animate">Ready to See What Your Team is *Really* Thinking?</h2>
            <p class="cta-subtitle scroll-animate">
                Stop chasing survey scores. A 15-minute demo of Hoogly will show you how to get the 
                actionable, qualitative insights you need to build a culture that retains top talent.
